{
  "stem": "9601.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] What other towns did you visit on your way to America after liberation?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, we were-- since we were Polish citizens, the Russians, you know, they had a political deal with the West or something.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they told us we can move to Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So people thought, you know, it's going to be like Poland before the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's not a-- it's not going to be communist.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As much as people accuse the Jews of being communists, 95-- 90% of the Jews did not subscribe to communist ideolog-- the idea-- now, you know the id-- of membership or something like that.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "From what I understand, it was a social and economic subscription.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "First of all, at least you were not persecuted.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybod-- Russian propaganda was or the idea-- ideology was, everybody is equal.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There is no ethnic discrimination.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Your-- everybody has equal rights.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's what Jews were looking for.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were not looking for making everybody equal and happy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they thought that Poland after the war would be like Poland before the war, which would be much nicer than being under communist.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No self expression.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No economic opportunities.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No regimentation.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from Poland, it was easier to leave Poland, go some place else other than Russia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So everybody jumped on the wagon, we went to Poland, came to Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Guess what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The communist sent power, which is we ended up in a city called Bytom, Upper, Silesia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's the Polish name not far from Katowice because you could take the street car from Bytom too.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nice town.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Very nice city.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Always liked it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the German name for it was Beuthen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I think it was not far on the Pole-- Germ-- Pole-- the border between Germany and Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because there was a big population-- big German population.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
